Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When you were younger, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,your parents were probably the first ones \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.31,0:00:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you ran to for advice.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.02,0:00:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But now you might feel \Nthat your parents \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.06,0:00:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,just don’t understand you.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep down, \Nyou still want to talk to them. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if you try, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.40,0:00:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and you feel \Nthey just aren’t listening?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you could raise your voice, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.81,0:00:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but shouting won’t make \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,your parents more receptive \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and won’t show them \Nthe respect they deserve.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.98,0:00:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You could give your parents \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the silent treatment, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.15,0:00:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Bible suggests \Nat Proverbs 15:22 \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that things only get more frustrating \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,when you don’t talk.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So saying nothing \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,really gets you nowhere. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s smarter to just wait \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,for a better time to talk.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:00:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you might even write them \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:00:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,an honest but respectful letter \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.15,0:01:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,expressing how you feel. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if the situation is flipped? \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that’s right. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.19,0:01:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your parents want to talk, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.81,0:01:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but you don’t.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you had a bad day at school. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.94,0:01:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s true that choosing to talk \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,when you don’t feel like it could mean \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the conversation will be forced, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,which makes everyone tense \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and leads to poor communication.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But refusing to talk \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,means you’ll still be stressed, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and your parents might think \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that the problem is bigger than it is, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,or worse, \Nthat you’re hiding something.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, you could start off \Ntalking with them \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,on a subject that isn’t as stressful \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,or even one that makes you happy.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That will ease the tension \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,or get rid of it all together.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The bottom line: \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.44,0:01:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your parents want to help you \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can use their help.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So choose your words carefully, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:01:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,deliver them respectfully, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and think of your parents as friends, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,not enemies.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because let’s face it, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you’ll need all the allies \Nyou can get to cope \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,with the challenges that lie ahead.\N
